Metadata-Version: 1.0
Name: fifslack-bitbucket-pr-reminder
Version: 0.0.3
Summary: Posts a Slack reminder with a list of open pull requests for an organization
Home-page: http://github.com/ordenador/fifslack-bitbucket-pr-reminder
Author: Mario Faundez
Author-email: mariofaundez@hotmail.com
